{"word":"ὑπεκδύομαι","slug":"ὑπεκδύομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὑπεκδύομαι</b></el> <p/><a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a>, with aor2 <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a>, <i>to slip out of, escape</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>; <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b>; <a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a>, <el>ὑπεκδύς</el> <i>having slipped out</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/>"}]}